  "text": [
    "Believe it or not,",
    "the old woman said,",
    "and I tried to picture it:",
    "a girl,",
    "the polished white ribs of a roast",
    "tied to her boots with twine,",
    "the twine coated with candle wax",
    "so she could glide",
    "uninterrupted",
    "across the ice\u2014",
    "my mother,",
    "skating on bones."
  ],
  "title": "Tintype on the Pond, 1925",
